"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-showbiz-celine-dion-spotted-ahead-paris-2024-olympic-ceremony-b1172491.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Showbiz  Sign up to our free weekly newsletter for exclusive competitions, offers and theatre ticket deals    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Celine Dionfuelled speculation she will make her musical comeback at the 2024Paris Olympicswhen she was pictured greeting fans in the French capital.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9913259052403215, \"rank\": 0.007679334084866085, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 56-year-old has not performed live since disclosing her rare stiff person syndrome (SPS), which causes progressive muscular inflexibility.\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 0.6402557589156562, \"rank\": 0.5614189197951112, \"text\": \"SPS\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday,Variety first reported thatthe Grammy award winning star arrived in Paris ahead of the Games along with US singer Lady Gaga.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.006894369872458e-16, \"text\": \"Variety\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\"}, {\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.188793371269418e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9969026794121147, \"rank\": 0.0018886945020193133, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just hours later, she was then pictured arriving to her hotel and seen greeting fans outside, fuelling the rumours.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadian singer previously teased that a comeback may be imminent in an April interview.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.7395208350191151, \"rank\": 0.29922745655705413, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She toldVogue Franceat the time: \\\"I have chosen to work with all my body and soul, from head to toe, with a medical team.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to be the best I can be.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My goal is to see the Eiffel Tower again!\\\"\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The hitmaker, who revealed her SPS diagnosis in 2022 as she cancelled her Courage World Tour, said she was working everyday to get back on stage.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1318, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 0.6402557589156562, \"rank\": 0.5614189197951112, \"text\": \"SPS\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courage_World_Tour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Courage World Tour\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courage_World_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courage_World_Tour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"For four years I have been saying to myself that I am not going back, that I am ready, that I am not ready\\u2026 As things stand, I can not stand here and say to you: 'Yes, in four months'.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know\\u2026 My body will tell me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would not be Dion's first Olympics peformance, having previously opened the Games in Atlanta, Georgia in 1996 with her track The Power of the Dream.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999978062988, \"rank\": 2.1789763549265313e-09, \"text\": \"Atlanta, Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}, {\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999978062988, \"rank\": 2.1789763549265313e-09, \"text\": \"Atlanta, Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Standard has contacted Celine Dion's rep for comment.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.37499476039726e-41, \"text\": \"The Standard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\"}, {\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.903845700590196e-38, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In light of the reports, French PresidentEmmanuel Macronsays he would be \\\"immensely happy\\\" if Dion attended the Paris Olympics 2024 opening ceremony, which will take place in front of the famous Parisian landmark.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked about the news, Macron told France 2 in French: \\\"Apparently, she (Dion) has arrived in Paris.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2128, \"end\": 2134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 0.9999999288625102, \"rank\": 7.113727095126288e-08, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 2152, \"end\": 2158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9913259052403215, \"rank\": 0.007679334084866085, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.188793371269418e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's great.\\\"\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Starmer: Trump tariffs over Greenland 'wrong' and UK 'pursuing this' with US  Cooper praises courage of protesters in Iran in the face of violent crackdown  No 10 defends military funding amid warnings of \\u00a328bn black hole  Get ahead with expert services designed to boost business development  When asked about her participating in the ceremony, Macron said it would be \\\"fantastic news\\\" if she did, because Dion is \\\"a great artist\\\".\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2248, \"end\": 2257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenland\", \"score\": 0.9999999960859896, \"rank\": 3.903256217126747e-09, \"text\": \"Greenland\", \"